---
// Section 3: Transforming School Dining
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <h2
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light leading-tight text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 text-text-heading leading-relaxed max-w-5xl mx-auto"
    >
      Transformamos el comedor escolar en una experiencia de sabores y salud.
    </h2>

    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Card 1: Balanced Menus -->
      <div
        class="bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <h3
          class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-tight mb-8 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Menús equilibrados y adaptados a cada etapa escolar
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <img
            src="/images/ilustraciones-01.svg"
            alt="ilustración 1"
            width="200"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Professional Team -->
      <div
        class="bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <h3
          class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-tight mb-8"
        >
          Un equipo de cocineros y nutricionistas comprometidos
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <img
            src="/images/ilustraciones-02.svg"
            alt="ilustración 2"
            width="200"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Fresh Ingredients -->
      <div
        class="bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <h3
          class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-tight mb-8 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Ingredientes frescos y de proximidad
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <img
            src="/images/ilustraciones-03.svg"
            alt="ilustración 3"
            width="200"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Educational Methodology -->
      <div
        class="bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <h3
          class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-tight mb-8 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Metodología lúdica y educativa
        </h3>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <img
            src="/images/ilustraciones-04.svg"
            alt="ilustración 4"
            width="200"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
